00:19:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote></blockquote><br />\n佢wtsapp係hea回你定係都正正常常？<br />\n你本身係完全唔識佢？<br />\n係咪讀緊同一科？ 或者有冇共同活動平台？[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n都算正常既 我諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n本身完全唔識呀 係無啦啦唔知點解咁有勇氣走去問人 咁大個仔第一次咁做<br />\n近排仲要exam 好似阻住哂人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/quote]<br />\n還掂都開大左個頭<br />\n唔差在約埋佢溫書 還者約佢考完試去玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1429411cd9bc6529ab69c984fdb3b44e30c6fc4","tid":30931,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇完我個名  有咩感覺 ?</blockquote><br />\n起碼仲有路行先啦<br />\n可能行行下有彎轉呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"261927fbc005814325d47f50a49f6d60e4f495c3","tid":30931,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:22:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩有條撚樣打黎我無聽<br />\n我打返過去 佢問我係邊位 <br />\n重要勁惡咁叫我諗清楚先打過去<br />\nOn撚9 無拿拿比人話</blockquote><br />\n可能佢有急事 打錯電話<br />\n當佢焦慮/煩躁緊個時又有個唔識嘅人打黎<br />\n佢心情唔好先會咁姐<br />\n俾佢話兩句姐 又唔係打你<br />\n你咪當有個痴線佬 可憐下佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c3ef3d57d61f9f2c00c017ad9a00afc370684c","tid":30931,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申17dse<br />\n溫書溫到好氣餒，連屋企人都唔比支持我，潑我冷水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 覺得一直都得自己一個，好灰心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記住讀書係為自己 就算冇人支持你都要撐住自己 其實唔止讀書 任何事都一樣<br />\n你過多幾年都接近出黎社會做事嘅階段 要開始學習獨立 有問題要自己嘗試解決先 唔得先搵人幫拖<br />\n你自己讀唔掂咪試下問同學仔囉 我總唔信個個同學都咁自私 同人多啲交流對溫書好有幫助<br />\n仲有，人地愈睇死你，你就愈要自強，我同你講，如果因為冇人支持你而hea左個study leave嘅話，冇人會可憐你，而你第時條路都唔易行。<br />\n<br />\n利申 以前冇認真讀書 後來讀part time degree好撚辛苦"},{"pid":"f9ac6023574f0341af3e9996daf271a28b89b17a","tid":30931,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:32:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我好唔開心 kfc個芝士撻我食到上哂癮<br />\n依加唔食會口痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過啲流心芝士同無骨鳳爪係點整？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96f55543f35380b1984513099c573ba424eb5214","tid":30931,"uid":62025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:33:51.000Z","msg":"多謝樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76e512401a93db14e1cee70a7f158f28f9c1e4cb","tid":30931,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成日都做膠野，岩岩apply 工都可以睇錯野</blockquote><br />\n我返工都成日做錯啲on9野<br />\n例如出email會漏attachment<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之前轉工填application form 自己生日填左2016年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唯有以後做完啲野要認真check一次先 唔好媽虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d348a3774401fa52319ea1bde9f4f191226a8e","tid":30931,"uid":31938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:37:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>差緊人好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁努力賺錢 同埋唔好咁大洗 加油</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有咩好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e2f19f123bbd6a42953a14ad7185bbfdcf3135","tid":30931,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:41:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽日final 可以講咩都唔識</blockquote><br />\n原因係自己懶冇溫書？<br />\n還是係有努力過 但真係讀唔掂？"},{"pid":"4ac1397b50621dc8c51473804d77a6c98a79819e","tid":30931,"uid":35644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T00:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好難忘記舊公司</blockquote><br />